            "DisplayOrder": 550,
            "DialogCategory": 8,
            "DialogCondition": 0,
            "GroupId": 4,
            "ActionName": "",
            "DialogType": 0,
            "Duration": 11900,
            "LocalizeKR": "올려다볼 때마다,\n선생님의 얼굴이 떠올라.",
            "LocalizeJP": "見上げる度に、\n先生の顔が浮かぶの。",
